@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam maxMessageSize 180

actor "Nguoi dung" as User
participant "LoginView\n(View)" as View
participant "LoginController" as Controller
participant "AuthService" as Service
participant "AccountRepository" as Repository
database "MySQL\n(BoardingHouse_DB)" as DB

Note over User, DB: QUY TRINH DANG NHAP VA PHAN QUYEN

User -> View : 1. Nhap username/password va bam Dang nhap
View -> Controller : 2. login(username, password)
activate Controller

Controller -> Service : 3. authenticate(username, password)
activate Service

Service -> Repository : 4. findByUsername(username)
activate Repository
Repository -> DB : 5. SELECT tai_khoan theo username
activate DB
DB -->> Repository : 6. Account row
Repository -->> Service : 7. Optional<Account>
deactivate DB
deactivate Repository

Service -> Service : 8. Kiem tra mat khau hien tai (so sanh truc tiep)

alt Hop le
    Service -->> Controller : 9. Account (ADMIN/NHAN_VIEN)
    Controller -->> View : 10. Mo dashboard theo role
else Khong hop le
    Service -->> Controller : 11. IllegalArgumentException
    Controller -->> View : 12. Hien thi thong bao loi
end

deactivate Service
deactivate Controller
@enduml
